{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/pai_smile.png?t=1737669259\" /> Good morning! I am PAI - your Personal AI - and I am here to assist you!<br><br>I apologize for awakening you early, <strong>but you have slept through the end of the world!</strong><br><br>But don't panic, I am here to help! With me and your trusty protosuit, you'll be able to <strong>mine ores and build an underground base to live in!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/mining.gif?t=1737669259\" /><br><br>There might not be sunshine down here, but at least you're not alone. I've located several other survivors you can <strong>wake up and bring to your newly constructed base!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/rig.gif?t=1737669259\" /><br><br>But, if you want to reach the surface, you'll have to do more than just survive. You'll need to:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Expand and automate your base...</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/automation.gif?t=1737669259\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Get help from familiar faces...</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/meet_prof.gif?t=1737669259\" /><br><br>And, I don't want to alarm you, but I'm detecting <strong>creatures down here that are definitely NOT native to Earth!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795570/extras/wyrm.gif?t=1737669259\" /><br><br>While I might not be programmed to deal with post-apocalyptic scenarios, I'm certain humanity is safe in my capable hands. <strong>With a little help from you of course!</strong><br><br><strong>Aground Zero is a 3D spinoff of our previous game, Aground. It takes place during the same events of the original game, although knowledge of Aground is not necessary to play.</strong><br><br><strong>NOTE:</strong> Only one player can use the keyboard and mouse for local co-op - every other player (supports up to four) must have a separate controller (but all four can use controllers if desired).","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Powering Up","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1795570/a415f5d28b86278719cda3f38517b00815325533.jpg"},{"name":"Instant Meat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1795570/b52c2225966ab21e410e4bdc56f929205e155f9f.jpg"},{"name":"Shelter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1795570/4205c9f5a6efe721ee00ae05b64e38fd9a834190.jpg"},{"name":"Shiny","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1795570/2cf7c299e90664ef2d3f4885f2fa551706487ae3.jpg"},{"name":"Upgrade Complete","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1795570/135df00991f8507860ce9a2c4b27c944acfdf589.jpg"},{"name":"Good Morning!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1795570/43d5588eb9e2095014fdcf945306dbb26d3cb76e.jpg"},{"name":"Familiar Face","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1795570/6206ca5f0328cd75647c83068239ddc88001d8e1.jpg"},{"name":"Wyrmslayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1795570/90c1ac16d7b9b072150ed8e61334b9da19f7d2a5.jpg"},{"name":"Mmm, Cheese","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1795570/f14f952cfc4400364111048dcdd45133b9727ce4.jpg"},{"name":"Transportation Network","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1795570/58bf3d60ab1b64ca7c1f9dfc02b88d4cee82eeff.jpg"}],"total":33},"background":"https://shared